    "7228614": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "The story is quite complete, but it's lacking some emotional turmoil. Hmm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Xavier?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What's on your mind?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Heavens forgive me, I'm a real souse this morning, I am. I left my friend in the restaurant after completely forgetting about them!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "But I think I can now write an all-new, presentable script now and give this one more shot. It'll definitely work this time. No, I'll make it work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Please allow me a little more time. Just one day will suffice."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "*sigh*... But it's going to be tricky with those two actors. Ms. Koharu and Mr. Sasano don't seem keen on trying again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "But I can't blame them either. I'll just have to think of something when the time comes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Can I help in any way?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "No, no, no, I couldn't ask for anything more comforting than having you here to listen to me vent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "#My dear {NICKNAME}, you are indeed a great listener."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Ms. Paimon, if my behavior was at all untoward just now, can you forgive me? I didn't mean you any offense."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh? \"Ms. Paimon\"... That has a nice ring to it! Alright then, the magnanimous Paimon has decided to forgive you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Wonderful! I feel much better now. Let's meet tomorrow at <color=#00E1FFFF>Komore Teahouse</color>. I'll bring an even better script, you'll see!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "It's great that he's so motivated, but it's like Mr. Okazaki said... Is it really okay for him to do it all by himself?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "He says he's gonna write a brand-new script in one day. That's a scary big job, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'd like to help him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hmm, maybe you should let Xavier work out the script by himself. Paimon thinks we can help him with his actor problem instead."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'll go talk to the actors."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, that should take a load off his back."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
