    "7228701": {
        "Desc": "Look for the two performers and talk to them",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "You're the one who was involved in the screening, you're..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "Yes, I'm so sorry, I didn't remember your name."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "It's my fault for having a faulty memory. Sorry I gave you guys a hard time when we were filming."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "I know Xavier is from Fontaine. My most important person is also an outlander, so I understand how difficult it is to be alone in a foreign land."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "I was picky in the past and caused him trouble. Looking back on it pricks at my conscience."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We still need actors."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "Is this what Mr. Xavier wants? Th-Then please allow me to participate."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "I was called in to participate in the shooting before, though I was only paid the price of a meal. But money that's paid is paid, so I will finish what I started."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just go to <color=#00E1FFFF>Komore Teahouse</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "Got it. I'll go tell my family later that I'm going to the <color=#00E1FFFF>Komore Teahouse</color>."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7228702": {
        "Desc": "Look for the two performers and talk to them",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "#You've come, {NICKNAME}? I know it is rude to say this, but..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "I'm sorry! May I ask if Mr. Xavier still needs an actress?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "I left in a rage, and failed Master in her painstaking efforts of expressing concern as well as messing up the quest given by the head of the family. I have disgraced the Yashiro Commission."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "Master has reprimanded me, so please, I beseech you, please mention this to Xavier so I may do my duty."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What did Furuta say to you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "No, no, Master only asked me to think about why I want to stay with the Yashiro Commission."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "I made a vow to the head of the family and to the Kamisato Clan that I would never do anything detrimental to the name of the Kamisato Clan in a fit of pique."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "I was too reckless, and indolent, and as a Shuu... no, as a servant of the Kamisato Clan, I was very much out of line."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "And Mr. Xavier was actually very kind to me. Once again, I... I'm so sorry!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You don't have to be so anxious."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We still need actors."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "You mean I still have a chance, and I can go and apologize to Mr. Xavier to make up for my mistake?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "Wonderful, wonderful! I must do well this time. Your generosity is appreciated."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Just go to <color=#00E1FFFF>Komore Teahouse</color>."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "I'll set out right away after I've tidied up my appearance."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
