    "7228716": {
        "Desc": "Head to the designated location",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Good. You all said your lines naturally and didn't make any mistakes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Wait, they left already?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "I added more lines for them. And even used their real names for the characters after obtaining their permission..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "#Ignore those bullies. If it hadn't been for {NICKNAME}, this scene wouldn't have been shot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's nothing."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't mention it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "#{NICKNAME}, you're too modest."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "You delivered a smooth performance in that scene. Keep up this level and the next big scene will be no problem at all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "Oh yes, there is one more scene next."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Yes, I thought about it yesterday when I wrote the script, and this last scene must be shot in a place with a cliff. The <color=#00E1FFFF>small island</color> to the east of <color=#00E1FFFF>Narukami Island</color> is very suitable."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Well, this next scene on location is the key to the whole script, and I want to use the <color=#00E1FFFF>glow of sunset</color> as the backdrop."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "All of us have been shooting continuously for a long time, so we should take this time to rest. Let's meet <color=#00E1FFFF>tomorrow evening</color> at the designated location."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "7228717": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Xavier",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "The third act requires a little more from Mr. Sasano. This new character, Wakayama Kojuurou, is Wakayama Keisuke's younger brother and it is more appropriate to have Mr. Sasano play him."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "#You told me before, and I am mentally prepared. It's just... remember to pull your punches for that second fight scene, {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "#Oh yes, the script! I forgot to hand the script to {NICKNAME}."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "Look at me, all I'm thinking about is how to shoot the next scene and I forgot to give you the script. I am so sorry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "With past experiences from the first scenes, I believe you are already familiar with the way we shoot."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#Huh? {M#He}{F#She} has to jump off a cliff at the end? That's really dangerous."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It's fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yeah, you're used to jumping off high places and stuff, but now that you're doing it before a Film Kamera, you need to act more realistically."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And if that gets you into an accident, Paimon guesses it wouldn't be worth it, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We have a wind glider."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon knows you're used to facing all sorts of danger but you cannot think of yourself as an invincible person made of steel."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Xavier",
                    "T": "#Dear Miss Paimon, we do not need {NICKNAME} to jump off a cliff here. {M#He}{F#She} just needs to glide down the cliff using a wind glider."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Don't worry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, if you say so..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Then go for it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Koharu",
                    "T": "Go!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sasano",
                    "T": "Go!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
